---
title: Romesco Beef & Roast Veggie Rice with Garlic Yoghurt & Almonds
description: To give this comforting dish a pop, we're infusing beef strips with Spanish-style flavours by coating them with rustic romesco sauce.
Served over a bed of nourishing roasted veggies that are tossed through rice, this will leave you feeling pleasantly full and satisfied.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/romesco-beef-roasted-veggie-rice-3c4b3f58.jpg
